#. <section class="sutta" id="sn38.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Assāsappattasutta → assāsasuttaṃ (bj) | assāso (pts1)
msgctxt "sn38.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Assāsappattasutta"
msgstr "5. Solace"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn38.5:1.1"
msgid "“‘Assāsappatto, assāsappatto’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘gaining solace’."

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, assāsappatto hotī”ti?"
msgstr "At what point do you gain solace?”"

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, āvuso, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca "
"assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ettāvatā kho, āvuso, "
"assāsappatto hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“When a mendicant truly understands the six fields of contacts’ origin, "
"ending, gratification, drawback, and escape, at that point they’ve gained "
"solace.”"

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for realizing this solace?”"

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti."
msgstr "“There is.” …"

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.6"
msgid ""
"“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā, etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.7"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāya, "
"seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.8"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.9"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā, etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.10"
msgid ""
"“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā, etassa assāsassa sacchikiriyāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.5:1.11"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.5:1.12"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
